name: Digital Video Syndicate
overview:
The mission of DVS is producing and distributing premium branded video content to online community leaders and their audiences.

DVS specializes in video seeding, SEO campaigns and video production.

Led by an experienced group of ex-network television producers, DVS has produced video based campaigns for clients that include brands (Honda, Acura, Gillette, TD Ameritrade), agencies, political campaigns, non-profits and e-commerce (specializing in the self storage industry).
